import React from "react";

const Logo = () => (
  <svg width="50%" height="50%" viewBox="0 0 500 550" version="1.1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <title>Group</title>
      <desc>Created with Sketch.</desc>
      <defs></defs>
      <g id="Page-1" stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd">
          <g id="Group-3-Copy-4" transform="translate(-250.000000, -225.000000)" fill="#FFFFFF">
              <g id="Group" transform="translate(250.000000, 225.000000)">
                  <rect id="Rectangle" x="0" y="200" width="500" height="150"></rect>
                  <rect id="Rectangle" x="0" y="400" width="225" height="150"></rect>
                  <rect id="Rectangle" x="275" y="400" width="225" height="150"></rect>
                  <rect id="Rectangle" x="0" y="0" width="225" height="150"></rect>
                  <rect id="Rectangle" x="275" y="0" width="225" height="150"></rect>
              </g>
          </g>
      </g>
  </svg>
);

export default Logo;
